{"id":"mclaren","name_cn":"迈凯伦","name_en":"McLaren","country":"英国","region":"europe","founded_year":1963,"logo":"/logos/mclaren.svg","intro":"迈凯伦是英国超级跑车制造商，由传奇赛车手Bruce McLaren创立。品牌以F1赛车技术下放至公路跑车著称，碳纤维单体壳和轻量化设计是核心竞争力。","history":[{"year":1963,"event":"Bruce McLaren在英国创立McLaren车队"},{"year":1966,"event":"首次参加F1大奖赛"},{"year":1992,"event":"发布传奇超跑McLaren F1"},{"year":2010,"event":"成立McLaren Automotive，发布MP4-12C"},{"year":2013,"event":"发布旗舰混动超跑P1"}],"official_site":"https://www.mclaren.com","sources":[]}